data.description:
Fantastic Harvard Yale Home Now Available - This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home has so much to love...from the hardwood floors on the main level to the beautiful kitchen with granite counters, gas range and upgraded stainless steel appliances.  The Living Room and Dining Room have lots of windows and wood shutters.  A chandelier in the Dining Room is a nice addition.  A full bathroom is also on the main level with tile floors and nice tile   around the bath tub.Two bedrooms with ceiling fans are also on the main level.  The fully finished basement features an over-sized Family Room and a huge Master Bedroom with a glassed-in shower in the Master Bathroom.  Full-sized W/D units come with the home and are also downstairs.
The front and back lawns are fully landscaped.  The back yard is fenced.  A bonus is a large 2-car garage with lots of storage.
This home is located on a quiet neighborhood and a beautiful tree-lined street.  Sorry no pets.  For more information and a showing, email wpm@wasatchpm.com

No Pets Allowed

(RLNE3435112)
